Description:
    Generates an EzOnRails application. Has to be executed on a fresh rails application.
    Can also be used to update an EzOnRails application, by passing the --update flag.

Example:
    rails generate ezapp [APP_NAME]

    This will create:
        app/views/layouts/application.html.erb
        app/assets/stylesheets/application.scss
        app/views/shared/_breadcrumbs.html.erb
        app/views/shared/_dashboard.html.erb
        app/views/shared/_header.html.erb
        app/views/shared/_navigation.html.erb
        app/views/shared/_title.html.erb
        app/assets/images/logos/logo_left.png
        app/assets/images/logos/logo_right.png
        config/initializers/menu_structure_loader.rb
        config/menu_structure.json
